wn to be less\nthan one half or one third, we provide algorithms with small constant\ncompetitive ratios. We also propose algorithms with bounded competitive ratio\nin the case where the proportion of faulty robots is arbitrary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Dec 2017 02:31:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-08"}
