ue imaging. In addition to these applications, our study is of\ninterest for understanding spin dynamics in Kramers ions with nuclear spin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Dec 2017 15:48:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Jul 2018 18:42:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
